/wiki/FC_Litija: FC Litija is a futsal club from Litija , Slovenia .
/wiki/KMN_Puntar: Klub malega nogometa Puntar ( ) , commonly referred to as KMN Puntar or simply Puntar , is a futsal club based in Tolmin , Slovenia . The club was founded in 1974 .
/wiki/KMN_Kobarid: Klub malega nogometa Oplast Kobarid ( ) , commonly referred to as KMN Oplast Kobarid , is a futsal club from Kobarid , Slovenia .
/wiki/\u0160D_Brezje: Športno društvo Brezje Maribor or simply ŠD Brezje is a futsal club from Maribor , Slovenia . The club is also known as FutureNet Maribor due to sponsorship reasons .
/wiki/KMN_Dobovec: Klub malega nogometa Dobovec or simply KMN Dobovec is a futsal club from Rogatec , Slovenia .
